title: RAR for Android Premium v5.50 build 42 APK [SadeemPC]
description:
RAR for Android Premium v5.50 build 42
Requirements: Android 4.0+

RARLAB's RAR for Android can create RAR and ZIP and unpack RAR, ZIP, TAR, GZ, BZ2, XZ, 7z, ISO, ARJ archives. ZIP and RAR repair command. Benchmark function compatible with RARLAB's WinRAR benchmark.
